ed="T" n="0889b12"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0889b12"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>成都府法聚寺<persName key="A013834">員相</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0889b13"/><persName key="A013834">釋員相</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>人也。七歲出家，博綜內外，善屬<lb
ed="T" n="0889b14"/>文，時號<persName key="A013834">奇童</persName>。內修律範，人無間然。<date key="j19625821962877" notAfter-iso="+0662-01-27" notBefore-iso="+0661-04-07"><name>龍朔</name>元<lb
ed="T" n="0889b15"/>年</date>，有疾而終于<placeName key="PL000000034739">此寺</placeName>。將啟手足，房內長虹<lb
ed="T" n="0889b16"/>若練而飛上天，寺塔鈴索無風自鳴。其大<lb
ed="T" n="0889b17"/>門屋壁畫剝落，每夜有鼓角聲，經百餘日<lb
ed="T" n="0889b18"/>方息。從此鳥雀不棲其屋。<date key="j19668951967278" notAfter-iso="+0674-02-14" notBefore-iso="+0673-01-27"><name>咸亨</name>四年</date>，甘露<lb
ed="T" n="0889b19"/>降于講堂前<anchor xml:id="beg0889sgsz9"/>椶櫚<anchor xml:id="end0889sgsz9"/>樹焉。<persName key="A013834">相</persName>終，弟子收文集三<lb
ed="T" n="0889b20"/>十餘卷。寺中石像碑，<persName key="A013834">相</persName>作辭，<persName key="A013837">龔靈曠</persName>同撰，是<lb
ed="T" n="0889b21"/>歟。</p>
